{"tid":1730992,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"外國戰線：同蔡英文求救","createTime":"2019-11-17T15:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T17:21:18.000Z","uid":303641,"like":273,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"d0bdb07437f6ae09ebb1ea8933c3a1d8a33f0228","tid":1730992,"uid":303641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>如果你宜家坐響屋企唔知做咩，又過唔到去救手足。<br />\n請每一個宜家即刻打呢段template比蔡英文，炸爆佢嘅fb同email，記住，呢場有可能系人道浩劫！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統：<br />\n<br />\n香港自六月起，烽煙不絕。台港同氣連枝，一直為香港發聲，港人不勝銘感。<br />\n<br />\n自十一月起，香港警察多次進入校園，中大二號橋之戰更是令無數港人徹夜難眠。今天（17/11），港警包圍香港理工大學，示威者退無可退，展現『不自由，無寧死』的精神。<br />\n<br />\n入夜，數百示威者仍身在理工校園，被重重圍困。此情此景，如八九年的中國，六四事件正在重現。<br />\n<br />\n我們已退無可退，為了避免人道災難的重現，懇請蔡總統向國際及港府施以壓力，台港並肩，共度劫難。<br />\n<br />\n鈞鑒"},{"pid":"41b3c8234c524d8ec6df1e76eb394f491a2453bb","tid":1730992,"uid":125502,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L5J4Yo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL5J4Yo9.jpg&h=3a1a4096&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e403acdaeb469408bc95ea62661225d737d29132","tid":1730992,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a4895294c0e29fa5fe94ae51771b293fac078b","tid":1730992,"uid":30503,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"任何方法都要用喇"},{"pid":"e5d1cbe1e78f273dbc7bc699a44ae8917060f0ab","tid":1730992,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:38:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3936c84a8f4bf18b3206dc5a1b343291008930e6","tid":1730992,"uid":15812,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"d0bdb07437f6ae09ebb1ea8933c3a1d8a33f0228","tid":1730992,"uid":303641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"