ze: large;\"><strong>如果你宜家坐響屋企唔知做咩，又過唔到去救手足。<br />\n請每一個宜家即刻打呢段template比蔡英文，炸爆佢嘅fb同email，記住，呢場有可能系人道浩劫！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡總統：<br />\n<br />\n香港自六月起，烽煙不絕。台港同氣連枝，一直為香港發聲，港人不勝銘感。<br />\n<br />\n自十一月起，香港警察多次進入校園，中大二號橋之戰更是令無數港人徹夜難眠。今天（17/11），港警包圍香港理工大學，示威者退無可退，展現『不自由，無寧死』的精神。<br />\n<br />\n入夜，數百示威者仍身在理工校園，被重重圍困。此情此景，如八九年的中國，六四事件正在重現。<br />\n<br />\n我們已退無可退，為了避免人道災難的重現，懇請蔡總統向國際及港府施以壓力，台港並肩，共度劫難。<br />\n<br />\n鈞鑒"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">EMAIL:<br />\n<a href=\"https://service.president.gov.tw/newmailbox/write.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fservice.president.gov.tw%2Fnewmailbox%2Fwrite.aspx&d=sw6tlk2lcpT%2BYldK84vytKcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=c44e3e4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://service.president.gov.tw/newmailbox/write.aspx</a></div></span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"寫信俾小英"},{"pid":"8ddab2e4a5710d5051c57d551913674c8e347d67","tid":1730992,"uid":276744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"P 牌盡推"},{"pid":"ee7c4832bb1e96195dda46c517423bf86817750b","tid":1730992,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"15aee1717a67eefe7af7b8ccb05ca96ead626d5c","tid":1730992,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:09:25.000Z","msg":"頭先台灣都有個支援香港的集會<br />\n不過無時間睇"},{"pid":"0f55a60b46d0530d19ad0e08194239f4174643f6","tid":1730992,"uid":21260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"派兵"},{"pid":"9d8003fd962bd0341980582e6143a3cbac0fcd92","tid":1730992,"uid":329809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T16:09:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ssataline/status/1196096841995169792?s=19\" 